    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"page phb\" id=\"p10\" data-index=\"9\"><div class=\"columnWrapper\"><p><strong>Zenkai Boost:</strong> Starting at 7th level, your persistance in battle makes the beckoning light of the afterlife nothing but a boon for you to conquer. When you first reach 0 hit points and are healed to at least 1 hit point, you gain temporary hit points equal to twice your level and temporary chakra equal to half the amount. </p><p>Your primary jutsu casting modifiers, and their maximums, increase by +2, and any failed death saves you possess, are removed.You lose all benefits after 1 hour and can only activate this feature once per long rest.</p></div></div>",
